      <title>不到一半的美国银行准备向美联储紧急借款</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/less-than-half-us-banks-ready-borrow-fed-emergency-2024-04-12/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据美联储周五公布的数据，在硅谷银行倒闭一年后，只有不到一半的美国银行通过在美联储紧急贷款机构质押抵押品来建立借贷能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/less-than-half-us-banks-ready-borrow-fed-emergency-2024-04-12/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 12 Apr 2024 18:50:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
